<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AnalisAI | Inteligência em Análise Educacional</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/dashboard.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/sidebar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: 'helvetica', sans-serif;
            font-weight: normal;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        body.dash-body {
            background-color: #18181b;
        }

        .home-content-wrapper {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .card-elite {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 2px solid #2e3134;
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 40px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card-elite:hover {
            border-color: #444;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .card-line {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #ff0101;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }

        .icon-accent {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ff0101;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: block;
        }

        details {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 2px solid #2e3134;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        summary { list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; color: #fff; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        summary::after { content: '\f0fe'; font-family: 'Font Awesome 6 Free'; color: #ff0101; }

@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .main-layout {
        margin: 0 !important;
        padding: 20px !important;
    }
    .dash-header {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 30px !important;
    }

    .welcome-banner {
        padding: 40px 20px !important;
        margin-bottom: 40px !important;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .welcome-banner h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem !important;
    }

    .welcome-banner p {
        font-size: 1rem !important;
    }

    .dash-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
        gap: 20px !important;
    }

    .card-elite {
        padding: 30px 20px !important;
    }

    #sobre, #faq {
        margin-bottom: 60px !important;
    }

    .dash-footer {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
        text-align: center;
    }
}

@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .sidebar {
        width: 100%;
        height: 65px;
        flex-direction: row;
        top: auto;
        bottom: 0;
        padding: 0 10px;
        border-right: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #262626;
    }

    .sidebar-top, .sidebar-bottom {
        flex-direction: row;
        width: auto;
        gap: 5px;
    }

    .logo-container, 
    .divider, 
    .link-text, 
    .active-indicator {
        display: none !important;
    }

    .side-link {
        margin-bottom: 0;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .icon-box {
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .modal-new-card {
        width: 92%;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        border-radius: 24px;
    }

    .modal-new-card::before {
        width: 60px;
    }

    .modal-new-logo {
        width: 130px;
    }

    .modal-new-info-grid {
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .modal-new-text {
        font-size: 13px;
    }

    .main-layout {
        margin-left: 0 !important;
        margin-bottom: 65px !important;
    }
}

@media screen and (max-width: 380px) {
    .sidebar {
        padding: 0 5px;
    }
    .icon-box {
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
    }
}
    </style>
</head>
<body class="dash-body">
    <%- include('partials/header') %> 

    <div class="main-layout">
        
        <div class="home-content-wrapper">
            
            <header class="dash-header" style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); margin-bottom: 40px;">
                <div class="header-left">
                    <img src="/IMG/logo3-white.png" alt="AnalisAI" style="height: 35px;">
                </div>
                <div class="header-user">
                    <div class="header-actions">
                        <a href="/login" class="btn-secondary-dash" style=" color: #fff;">
                            ACESSAR PAINEL
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </header>

            <main>
                <section id="inicio" class="welcome-banner" style="padding: 100px 60px; border-radius: 30px; margin-bottom: 80px; position: relative;">
                    <div class="banner-text">
                        <h1 style="font-size: 4rem; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                            SISTEMA DE <br> ANÁLISE DE AVANÇOS
                        </h1>
                        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 600px; opacity: 0.9;">
                            Organize competências, monitore frequências e alcance objetivos educacionais com a precisão de dados em tempo real.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section id="sobre" style="margin-bottom: 100px;">
                    <h2 class="section-title-2" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">PILARES ESTRATÉGICOS</h2>
                    <div class="dash-grid">
                        <div class="card-elite">
                            <div class="card-line"></div>
                            <i class="fas fa-university icon-accent"></i>
                            <h3 style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">SENAI CIC</h3>
                            <p style="color: #888; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">Referência em formação profissional, o SENAI CIC atua como hub tecnológico preparando talentos para a Indústria 4.0.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card-elite">
                            <div class="card-line"></div>
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-line icon-accent"></i>
                            <h3 style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">ANÁLISE DE DADOS</h3>
                            <p style="color: #888; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">Transformamos avaliações complexas em indicadores visuais claros para identificar a aptidão de cada estudante.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card-elite">
                            <div class="card-line"></div>
                            <i class="fas fa-bullseye icon-accent"></i>
                            <h3 style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 15px;">RESULTADOS</h3>
                            <p style="color: #888; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">Acompanhe a evolução das turmas e garanta o sucesso acadêmico com decisões baseadas em dados organizados.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section id="faq" style="margin-bottom: 120px; max-width: 800px;">
                    <h2 class="section-title-2" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">DÚVIDAS FREQUENTES</h2>
                    <div class="faq-container">
                        <details>
                            <summary>Como o nível do aluno é calculado?</summary>
                            <p style="color: #666; padding-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem;">O sistema cruza a nota (mínima 7.0) com a presença (mínima 75%) para definir o status.</p>
                        </details>
                        <details>
                            <summary>O sistema é exclusivo para o SENAI?</summary>
                            <p style="color: #666; padding-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem;">Sim, é uma ferramenta personalizada para otimização de fluxos internos do SENAI CIC.</p>
                        </details>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </main>

            <footer class="dash-footer">
            <div class="footer-credits">
                <p>© 2026 AnalisAI
            </div>
        </footer>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>